nodes.text: Star Wars Jedi Quest Kids Club 3

Star Wars Jedi Quest Kids Club 3 was the third and final issue of Star Wars Jedi Quest Kids Club Magazine. It was published by Hasbro Inc. in November 2000. The final issue featured twenty-three pages of content, ranging from articles on the Jedi Council to new Star Wars action figures.
